               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>Production unit I</p>
                     <p>Collection of mälkǝˀ-poems </p>
                     <p>I) መልክእ፡ ኢየሱስ“Mälkǝˀ-Hymn for Jesus Christ” (fols. <locus from="3r" to="15r"/>) II) መልክእ፡ ማርያም“Mälkǝˀ-Hymn for the Virgin Mary” (fols. <locus from="15r" to="34r"/>) </p>
                     <p>Production unit II</p>
                     <p>III) መጽሐፈ፡ ኑዛዜ“Book of Confession” (fols. <locus from="36r" to="45v"/>), a penitential in Amharic with admixture of Gǝˁǝz, possibly incomplete.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
                
               </msContents>
