                           <p>Deficient. The original sewing of the manuscript has been crudely repaired with recent threads. Quire VI is attached to the text block with threads led through the holes for tackets.  Fols. <locus from="13" to="16"/>, <locus from="17" to="24"/> and <locus from="37" to="45"/> are damaged by rodents. The text is partly abraded on fols. <locus from="1v" to="2v"/>, <locus from="10v" to="11r"/>, <locus target="#16"/>. Fols. <locus from="32v" to="35r"/> are discoloured.</p>
                           
